# YAMDOG <!-- omit in toc -->

Yet Another Markdown Only Generator

## Examples

> |  a  |  b  |                       $\leq$                      |
> | :-- | :-: | ------------------------------------------------: |
> |  1  |  2  | [$\leq$](https://www.snakemd.io/en/latest/usage/) |
> |  3  |  4  |                         5                         |
> |  7  |  8  |                         9                         |

- Just a text
- Sublist
    - a
    - b
- > |  a  |  b  |                       $\leq$                      |
  > | :-- | :-: | ------------------------------------------------: |
  > |  1  |  2  | [$\leq$](https://www.snakemd.io/en/latest/usage/) |
  > |  3  |  4  |                         5                         |
  > |  7  |  8  |                         9                         |
- second sublisting, definition
    : First definition
    : Second definition
